    "An illustration of two extreme configurations is presented in Fig. 1a, c, where we consider the local intra-order hyperedge overlap of a node i with a generalized 2-degree k ð2Þ i = 4.",
    "In Fig. 1a, we show the configuration in which the number of unique neighbors of node i is at its maximum, i.e., S ð2Þ i = S ð2Þ, + i = 8, resulting in T ð2Þ i = 0.",
